com.google.cloud.compute

Class SubnetworkInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.google.cloud.compute.SubnetworkInfo
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    Subnetwork

    public class SubnetworkInfo
extends Object
implements Serializable
    A Google Compute Engine subnetwork. Compute Engine subnetworks allow you to segment your Compute Engine network IP space into subnetworks. Subnetworks for a Compute Engine network can be automatically allocated, or you can create a custom topology.
    See Also:
    Subnetworks, Serialized Form

        public String getIpRange()
